Summary: Orange lights flying in sky over Thurston County.
divs: Sighting Detailswe were at a party of around 125 people and we were lighting off fireworks, and we saw these steady moving fire balls, they were not flickering, just one after another, total of around 5 , no noise, same speed, same path, very strange. Were not fire works , we tried to take a picture, but they would not show up on our camera. I have seen reports all over about these things. Have you heard what they are?
trends: There have been 82 other sightings in Washington
There were no other sightings in Washington on or around July 4th 2010
